Generic single-database configuration.

The four exploratory migrations on `main` (f2cf858fa59b, 00c3bfdb60bf,
233d6687abde, 0baa9d994af2) have been collapsed into a single
`0001_initial_schema.py` as part of the rename to seekers/seances/
presences/whispers. If you have an existing local database that was
populated with the old chain, drop and recreate it before running
`alembic upgrade head`:

    docker compose down -v          # wipes the postgres volume
    docker compose up -d postgres
    alembic upgrade head
